<paragraph blockId="0.[1245,2126,688,879]" pageId="0" pageNumber="34">* Medium-sized, egg-laying mammals, completely lacking teeth, adapted for insectivorous or myrmecophagous diet, with robust, dome-shaped, spine-covered bodies and slender beaks.</paragraph>
