<paragraph blockId="0.[1246,2126,1122,1312]" pageId="0" pageNumber="34">* Mainly montane forests and alpine grasslands in New Guinea, but almost all terrestrial habitats in Australia.</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="0.[1246,2126,1122,1312]" box="[1246,1701,1244,1273]" pageId="0" pageNumber="34">s 2 genera, 4 species, 11 taxa.</paragraph>
